        "suggestion": "Make db/index.ts the raid-DB entry only (define/export getRaidDb and re-export schema.ts), and make consumers import user-DB things from a sibling barrel like '$lib/db/user' (which would re-export userSchema, users, userRecents, getUserDb). Mirrors the dual-config split (drizzle.config.ts vs drizzle.user.config.ts) at the import level.",
